data.description: Nice 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home. Family room, living room dining room and laundry room inside.  There is also a nice in-ground swimming pool for the hot summers. Home is pre-wired with 240V and ready for your spa. Home is located in the Country Meadows subdivision in SE Visalia.  This home needs a little TLC... Come see this home and let your imagination create that perfect environment for you. Solar PPA is linked to view in Documents.
